Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about speech recognition using an attention-based end-to-end model. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper deals with speech recognition. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper proposes a method to reduce delay in the encoder side. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper uses machine learning techniques for speech recognition. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper deals with an AI-based approach for speech recognition.
